video.title: Henry Danger
video.synopsis: A new part-time job forces Henry Hart to balance two lives, one as a typical teenager and the other as secret superhero sidekick Kid Danger.

episodes.synopsis: When Henry Hart applies for a novelty shop job, his skills are unexpectedly tested to see if he qualifies for the superhero-sized role of Kid Danger.
episodes.title: Episode 1

episodes.synopsis: After Henry becomes a sidekick-in-training to celebrated superhero Captain Man, he must adjust to his double life and face his first supervillain.
episodes.title: Episode 2

episodes.synopsis: While juggling Captain Man’s triple-beeps, school exams and house chores, Henry struggles to balance his old life and his new crime-fighting identity.
episodes.title: Episode 3

episodes.synopsis: Henry puts his job as Kid Danger at risk when he shares his secret with a trusted friend. Meanwhile, a titanium-toothed scoundrel is on the loose.
episodes.title: Episode 4

episodes.synopsis: After a perfume-spraying stranger strips Captain Man of his powers, Kid Danger and Charlotte work to defeat a mad scientist to reverse the effects.
episodes.title: Episode 5

episodes.synopsis: When Captain Man believes a suspicious Swellview High student is the son of a former foe, he goes undercover to find out the truth.
episodes.title: Episode 6

episodes.synopsis: When Jasper dresses up as Kid Danger and is kidnapped, a case of mistaken identity nearly ruins Halloween night.
episodes.title: Episode 7

episodes.synopsis: A massive space boulder lands at Junk-N-Stuff, where Ray learns that it’s an egg and must exterminate whatever creature crawls out.
episodes.title: Episode 8

episodes.synopsis: When an accusation leaves Henry outcasted from a birthday party, he disguises himself as a German sleuth to expose the real culprit.
episodes.title: Episode 9

episodes.synopsis: Swellview’s basketball coach recruits a new player, but Henry thinks the boy is unqualified to join the team. Meanwhile, the Man Cave is malfunctioning.
episodes.title: Episode 10

episodes.synopsis: A mysterious machine accidentally zaps Henry, making him unusually rude and barbaric -- just in time for a fancy dinner date with his ex-girlfriend.
episodes.title: Episode 11

episodes.synopsis: Turned invisible by a crazy mishap, Ray’s mischievous buddy goes to extremes to force Henry out as Kid Danger and become Captain Man's new sidekick.
episodes.title: Episode 12

episodes.synopsis: Henry and Ray deal with a new villain on a movie-spoiling spree ahead of a major premiere. Meanwhile, Piper goes all out to join Captain Man’s fan club.
episodes.title: Episode 13

episodes.synopsis: When a string of unusual burglaries hit a popular game show, Henry becomes a contestant to reveal a hypnotic ruse.
episodes.title: Episode 14

episodes.synopsis: With the threat of a volcano eruption looming over Swellview, Henry stands up to a terrifying bully and makes a move on his crush.
episodes.title: Episode 15

episodes.synopsis: After Bianca rejects Henry’s Valentine’s Day date, he escorts a human-like android to Club Soda to make her jealous. Captain Man dates Henry's teacher.
episodes.title: Episode 16

episodes.synopsis: The gang’s plans to celebrate Captain Man’s superhero anniversary are derailed when Jasper switches on emergency lockdown mode at the Man Cave.
episodes.title: Episode 17

episodes.synopsis: Not knowing the man behind the mask, Bianca shares an unexpected smooch with Kid Danger, sending Henry reeling over her betrayal.
episodes.title: Episode 18

episodes.synopsis: After Kris falls victim to a purse thief, Captain Man moves into the Harts residence to protect the family while Jake is away.
episodes.title: Episode 19

episodes.synopsis: Evil Dr. Minyak traps Henry in his dreams. Now, Ray, Charlotte and Schwoz must use extreme measures to wake Henry from his perpetual slumber.
episodes.title: Episode 20

episodes.synopsis: After Henry is grounded for sneaking out, Charlotte fills in temporarily as Kid Danger, causing tension between the friends.
episodes.title: Episode 21

episodes.synopsis: Piper and Jasper win a contest to explore Captain Man's secret Man Cave, but Henry worries his cover will be blown.
episodes.title: Episode 22

episodes.synopsis: Before Charlotte and Henry tell Jasper the truth about Kid Danger, they put his secret-keeping skills to the test. Jasper turns to Piper for help.
episodes.title: Episode 23

episodes.synopsis: While trying to catch a graffiti gang in Swellview, Kid Danger is seduced by a charming member of the crew. Jasper forms his own crime-fighting posse.
episodes.title: Episode 24

episodes.synopsis: Now running with Veronika and the Wall Dogs, Kid Danger fights with Captain Man. For Danger, his friends being bad begins to feel good.
episodes.title: Episode 25

episodes.synopsis: When Jasper brings his new girlfriend Courtney to town, she develops a crazy suspicion of Charlotte’s feelings for Jasper -- thanks to Henry.
episodes.title: Episode 26

episodes.synopsis: A mysterious birthday cake has not-sweet surprises in store for Kid Danger and Captain Man, as does a drastically different Charlotte.
episodes.title: The Beat Goes On

episodes.synopsis: Superpowers can't save Henry from an attack of girl trouble. Meanwhile, a mean granny hits Captain Man where it hurts.
episodes.title: One Henry, Three Girls: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: A school dance sets the stage for a busy night as Henry juggles identities, drama with Bianca and Chloe, and a big decision.
episodes.title: One Henry, Three Girls: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: Henry reluctantly agrees to coach Piper's underdog basketball team and meets his match with the strangely strict league board.
episodes.title: Henry and the Woodpeckers

episodes.synopsis: Ray heads out of town for a cousin's wedding, leaving Henry and Charlotte in charge of protecting Swellview. What could go wrong, right?
episodes.title: Captain Man: On Vacation

episodes.synopsis: Henry has an unforgettable day — over and over again — when he accidentally gets pulled into the villainous Time Jerker's mind-bending machine.
episodes.title: The Time Jerker

episodes.synopsis: When Henry is given a gift card for two to Swellview's swankiest restaurants, he's put in a sticky spot when Bianca and Ray both angle for an invite.
episodes.title: Secret Beef

episodes.synopsis: Jasper accidentally stops a crime and becomes the town hero, prompting a jealous Henry to rethink that whole secret identity thing.
episodes.title: Henry’s Jelly

episodes.synopsis: Captain Man and Henry find themselves on the wrong side of some weird local laws, landing them in jail on Christmas Eve.
episodes.title: Christmas Danger

episodes.synopsis: When Henry suffers an uncomfortable injury, Schwoz decides to use the Densitizer to make him indestructible — but there's a catch.
episodes.title: Indestructible Henry, Part 1

episodes.synopsis: The Densitizer gives Henry an unexpected and very inconvenient side effect, which he scrambles to hide from his family while investigating a cure.
episodes.title: Indestructible Henry, Part 2

episodes.synopsis: A cell phone video of Henry and Ray transforming into Kid Danger and Captain Man accidentally gets out, threatening to expose their secret identities.
episodes.title: Text, Lies, & Video

episodes.synopsis: A severe storm rains chaos when Henry and Charlotte are sent to an alternate universe, where their group's evil counterparts are up to no good.
episodes.title: Opposite Universe

episodes.synopsis: Impressed by Kid Danger and Captain Man, fellow superhero Phoebe Thunderman plans a meeting — and gets more than she expected.
episodes.title: Danger & Thunder Part 1

episodes.synopsis: In disguise, Kid Danger, Captain Man and Phoebe Thunderman infiltrate a secret meeting of villains that puts their powers to the test.
episodes.title: Danger & Thunder Part 2

episodes.synopsis: Gerta returns with new shapeshifter abilities, giving Henry a sneaky idea to get out of a family dinner so he can watch an MMA match.
episodes.title: Twin Henrys

episodes.synopsis: Ray is unsettled by unexplained happenings — like finding his underwear glued to the wall — and finds the culprit is someone he didn't see coming.
episodes.title: Grave Danger

episodes.synopsis: When a cookie infects Piper with a mysterious illness, Captain Man travels through time to the 1700s to find the only known cure.
episodes.title: Ox Pox

episodes.synopsis: Cryptic notes give Henry the sinking feeling his secret identity has been exposed. Meanwhile, Piper's new hustle gets messy.
episodes.title: I Know Your Secret

episodes.synopsis: When Ray and Henry let Jasper work at Junk N' Stuff, a mistake causes a party to buzz with trouble while Charlotte deals with the Auto Snacker.
episodes.title: A Fiñata Full Of Death Bugs

episodes.synopsis: Henry and Charlotte look into Ray's new girlfriend, Gwen, and her special muffins after Ray announces his surprise plan to get married.
episodes.title: Love Muffin

episodes.synopsis: After her invention for the Gizmo Show needs fixing, Charlotte worries that the repairs will reveal Henry and Ray's secret identities.
episodes.title: Scream Machine

episodes.synopsis: When a chip flavor contest divides Swellview, Captain Man and Kid Danger find themselves on opposite sides of the snack aisle.
episodes.title: The Trouble With Frittles

episodes.synopsis: As Ray and Henry struggle with their new podcast, Jasper's latest predicament turns out to be more than a false emergency.
episodes.title: Mouth Candy

episodes.synopsis: Henry needs help leaving class during a standardized test when he learns that Captain Man is stuck underground.
episodes.title: Gas Or Fail

episodes.synopsis: After a tough criminal named Drex escapes jail, Henry must figure out why Ray doesn't want him to help with the case.
episodes.title: Hour of Power Part 1

episodes.synopsis: With Captain Man caught in a jam, Henry gets a special opportunity to step up and stop Drex before the Man Cave gets ruined.
episodes.title: Hour of Power Part 2

episodes.synopsis: After Piper decides to take an anger management class, Ray and Henry make a bet on whether or not she will succeed.
episodes.title: JAM Session

episodes.synopsis: When Henry and his family are really sick at home, Schwoz scrambles to find a cure for a problem that he created.
episodes.title: Green Fingers

episodes.synopsis: Henry decides to try out his new talents in a dodgeball tournament with Jasper and Piper, but Ray wants to make sure his sidekick plays the right way.
episodes.title: Dodging Danger

episodes.synopsis: While Piper anxiously awaits for the TV to play her commercial, Captain Man and Kid Danger must save two astronauts trapped in a space station.
episodes.title: Space Invaders, Part 1

episodes.synopsis: Piper tries to pass the time before her commercial airs as Captain Man and Kid Danger learn why someone is holding two astronauts captive in space.
episodes.title: Space Invaders, Part 2

episodes.synopsis: Jasper and Henry both try to go out with Ms. Shapen's niece, but the final date turns out to be quite a toothy meal.
episodes.title: Double Date Danger

episodes.synopsis: To fly Captain Man's helicopter, Kid Danger must finish a mission alone. Elsewhere, Jasper, Piper and Charlotte get giddy over a cotton candy machine.
episodes.title: License to Fly

episodes.synopsis: As Captain Man and Kid Danger serve as judges for a talent show, they must figure out why contestants keep passing out during the performances.
episodes.title: Swellview’s Got Talent

episodes.synopsis: A chase after Jeff puts Captain Man and Kid Danger in the dark, forcing Charlotte and Jasper to lead a mission to find them.
episodes.title: Stuck In Two Holes

episodes.synopsis: Stalled at the Man Cave, Captain Man and Kid Danger must form a plan to rescue the Man Fans away from the watchful eye of rival Dr. Minyak.
episodes.title: Balloons Of Doom

episodes.synopsis: Internet celeb Frankini invites Captain Man and Kid Danger to a party, but the turnout isn't what they expected. Meanwhile, Charlotte babysits Piper.
episodes.title: Live & Dangerous: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: Charlotte, Schwoz, Jasper and Piper snap into action when Frankini announces his eye-opening plans for Captain Man and Kid Danger on a livestream.
episodes.title: Live & Dangerous: Part 2
